==FLOecology.org Architecture==

People 
*Community: JomSocial
*Experts: K2 user pages

Places 
*Profiles: GreenMap
*News Feeds: RSS2Content

Projects 
*K2 Categories 
*BEEx Clusters (eventually)

Participate 
*Updates: Newletter
*Join: Community
*Support: BEEx
*Volunteer: Opportunity Feed(?)

